              Computer System Technician-Networking 计算机系统技师-网络<br>
              Mechanical Engineering Technician-Design 机械工程技师-设计<br>
              Software Engineering Technician 软件工程技师<br>
              (Automotive) Motive Power Technician–Technical 汽车引擎技师-技术<br>
              Aviation Technician-Aircraft Maintenance 航空技师-飞机维护<br>
              Early Childhood Education  儿童早期教育<br>
              Game Art and Design   游戏设计和开发
            </div>

            <div>
              <strong>学士学位：</strong><br>
